name: Verify all existing and newly created Service`s categories and items are visible on Main page

steps.name: Verify Services tab "FirstCategory-0fd" is present on Main page

locator.isVisible(xpath=//section[.//*[text()='Сервіси' or text()='Services']]//a[@href="/first-service-0fd"][.//div[./span[@title="FirstService-0fd"]]/following-sibling::span[text()="First best service you have ever seen"]])
Verify FirstService-0fd service is present on Main page under the FirstCategory-0fd category

locator.isVisible(xpath=//section[.//*[text()='Сервіси' or text()='Services']]//a[@href="https://www.google.com/"][.//div[./span[@title="SecondService-0fd"]]/following-sibling::span[text()="Second best service you have ever seen"]])
Verify SecondService-0fd service is present on Main page under the FirstCategory-0fd category
Verify Services tab "SecondCategory-0fd" is present on Main page

locator.isVisible(xpath=//section[.//*[text()='Сервіси' or text()='Services']]//a[@href="/first-service-0fd"][.//div[./span[@title="FirstService-0fd"]]/following-sibling::span[text()="First best service you have ever seen"]])
Verify FirstService-0fd service is present on Main page under the SecondCategory-0fd category
